name: Laptops and Notebooks
description:
As a user
  I want to check functionality of laptop and notebook page

children.name: User should arrange product in price high to low order successfully
When I mouse hover and click on laptop and notebook tab
And I select menu "Show AllLaptops & Notebooks"
And I select product sort by "Price (High > Low)"
Then I should see product arrange in price high to low order successfully
User should place order successfully
When I mouse hover and click on currency dropdown
And I mouse hover and click on  £ Pound Sterling
When I mouse hover and click on laptop and notebook tab
And I select menu "Show AllLaptops & Notebooks"
And I select product sort by "Price (High > Low)"
And I select product "HP LP3065" from laptop and notebook page
And I should navigate to "HP LP3065" product
And I click on add to cart button
And I should see the message Success: You have added "HP LP3065" to your shopping cart!
And I click on shopping cart link into message
And I should see the shopping text message
And I should see the product name "HP LP3065"
And I change quantity "2" for product
And I click on update quantity
And I should see cart modified message
And I should see the total "£149.45"
And I click on checkout button
And I should navigate to checkout page

name: My Account Test
description:
As a user
  I want to check login/logout/register functionality

children.name: User should navigate to register page successfully
When I click on my account link
And I call the method selectMyAccountOptions method and pass the parameter "Register"
Then I should see text register account
User should navigate to login page successfully
When I click on my account link
And I call the method selectMyAccountOptions method and pass the parameter "Login"
Then I should see text returning customer
User should register account successfully
When I click on my account link
And I call the method selectMyAccountOptions method and pass the parameter "Register"
And I enter First Name "Kartik"
And I enter Last Name "Shah"
And I enter Email "kartik"
And I enter Telephone "81234567890"
And I enter Password "kartik8227"
And I enter Confirm Password "kartik8227"
And I select Subscribe Yes radio button
And I click on Privacy Policy check box
And I click on Continue button for registration
And I should see the message Your Account Has Been Created!
And I click on Continue button
And I click on my account link
And I call the method selectMyAccountOptions method and pass the parameter "Logout"
And I should see the text Account Logout
Then I click on Continue button
User should login and logout successfully
When I click on my account link
And I call the method selectMyAccountOptions method and pass the parameter "Login"
And I enter Email "prime123@gmail.com" on login page
And I enter password "kartik8227" on login page
And I click on login button
